entry.title: All four orbital launch pads fully loaded with rockets for the first time!
entry.summary:
All four orbital launch pads fully loaded with rockets for the first time!
SpaceX: SpaceX had four rockets on four pads and two Dragons on orbit today—as CRS-26 Dragon departed the @space_station with Crew-5 Dragon still attached to the orbiting lab, Falcon Heavy rolled out of the hangar, two Falcon 9’s readied for launch, and Ship 24 was stacked onto Booster 7
